<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">

  <PropertyGroup>
    <TargetFramework>netstandard1.6</TargetFramework>
    <Copyright>Bundled Sticks Inkorporated 2017</Copyright>
    <Version>2.4.0</Version>
    <AssemblyVersion>2.4.0.0</AssemblyVersion>
    <FileVersion>2.4.0.0</FileVersion>
    <Authors>Ethan Lafrenais;Tristan Smith</Authors>
    <PackageTags>Discord;Discord API</PackageTags>
    <Company>Bundled Sticks Inkorporated</Company>
    <Description>Discore provides a .NET Standard interface with Discord's HTTP, WebSocket, and voice APIs.
Please note: Discore is not an official Discord API interface!</Description>
    <PackageLicenseUrl>https://github.com/BundledSticksInkorperated/Discore/blob/master/LICENSE.md</PackageLicenseUrl>
    <PackageRequireLicenseAcceptance>True</PackageRequireLicenseAcceptance>
    <RepositoryUrl>https://github.com/BundledSticksInkorperated/Discore.git</RepositoryUrl>
    <RepositoryType>git</RepositoryType>
    <PackageProjectUrl>https://bundledsticksinkorperated.github.io/Discore/</PackageProjectUrl>
    <PackageReleaseNotes>- Removed DiscordHttpErrorCode.BadRequest.

- Fixed rate limited routes not taking major parameters into account.
- Fixed CreateInvite's maxAge argument causing a bad request.
- Fixed CreateGuildChannelParameters not treating all parameters as optional.
- Fixed DiscoreCacheTable.GetEnumerator throwing a NotImplementedException in some cases.

- Added ability to create guilds.
- Added missing DiscordPermission enum values.
- Added ability to set topic when creating text channels.
- Added missing Id property to OverwriteParameters.
- Added DiscoreTypeCache.Id.
- Added implicit Snowflake &lt;-&gt; ulong operator.
- Added DiscordHttpErrorCode enum value for error 50021.

And more...</PackageReleaseNotes>
